<div style="border:1px solid;">
 Attribute selector with specified value 
</div>

  <p class="para para1 para2"> paragraph shows attribute selector with ~ to select attribute with specified value as one the list of space seperated list of value  </p>  
<p style="background-color:#eee"> attribute selector with value as exactly as sepecified value followed by -
</p>
<p style="background-color:#111" > attribute selector with value that ends with specified value
